messages.content: What is ComfyUI YoloWorld-EfficientSAM?

ComfyUI YoloWorld-EfficientSAM is an unofficial implementation of YOLO-World + EfficientSAM for ComfyUI, which is a GUI that uses a stable diffusion model to generate images and videos. It utilizes YOLO-World and EfficientSAM to perform efficient object detection and segmentation.
What features are included in ComfyUI's Yoloworld ESAM èŠ‚ç‚¹?
Features of ComfyUI's Yoloworld ESAM include loading YOLO-World and EfficientSAM models, performing detection + segmentation, setting confidence threshold, IOU threshold, and more.
Can ComfyUI YoloWorld-EfficientSAM be used with video?
Yes, ComfyUI YoloWorld-EfficientSAM supports both image and video.
How to install ComfyUI YoloWorld-EfficientSAM?
ComfyUI YoloWorld-EfficientSAM can be installed either using ComfyUI Manager or manually by cloning the repository and installing the requirements.
What is YOLO-World?
YOLO-World is a fast and efficient object detection model.
What is EfficientSAM?
EfficientSAM is a model for visual perception tasks, specifically designed for instance segmentation.
How to update ComfyUI YoloWorld-EfficientSAM?
The project does not specify how to update the ComfyUI YoloWorld-EfficientSAM plugin. However, it is likely that updating would follow the same process as the initial installation.
Can ComfyUI YoloWorld-EfficientSAM be used with Impact-Pack?
Yes, the ðŸ”ŽYoloworld ESAM Detector Provider provided by [ltdrdata](https://github.com/ltdrdata) can be used together with Impact-Pack.
What is the latest version of ComfyUI YoloWorld-EfficientSAM?
The latest version, as of the provided documentation, is V2.0, which adds new features such as mask separation and extraction.
How to download EfficientSAM models?

The EfficientSAM models are available on the [EfficientSAM](https://huggingface.co/camenduru/YoloWorld-EfficientSAM/tree/main) GitHub page, where efficient_sam_s_cpu.jit and efficient_sam_s_gpu.jit can be downloaded.
